% Internal token list variables for thesis metadata
\tl_new:N \l__nusthesis_supervisor_tl
\tl_new:N \l__nusthesis_subtitle_tl
\tl_new:N \l__nusthesis_qualification_tl
\tl_new:N \l__nusthesis_keywords_tl

